{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Animation.onfinish","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\">Web Animations API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/Animation\"><code>Animation()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propiedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/currentTime\"><code>currentTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/effect\"><code>effect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finished\"><code>finished</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/id\"><code>id</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pending\"><code>pending</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playbackRate\"><code>playbackRate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/playState\"><code>playState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/ready\"><code>ready</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/replaceState\"><code>replaceState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/timeline\"><code>timeline</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><em><code>finish</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Animations</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationEffect\"><code>AnimationEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationPlaybackEvent\"><code>AnimationPlaybackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AnimationTimeline\"><code>AnimationTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/getAnimations\"><code>Document.getAnimations()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/timeline\"><code>Document.timeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentTimeline\"><code>DocumentTimeline</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element/animate\"><code>Element.animate()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/KeyframeEffect\"><code>KeyframeEffect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>La propiedad <code>onfinish</code> de la interfaz <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a> (de la <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Animations API (en-US)</a>) es el manejador de eventos para el evento <code><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/Reference/Events/finish\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">finish</a></code>. Este evento se envía cuando la animación termina de reproducirse.</p>\n<p>El evento <code>finish</code> ocurre cuando la reproducción se completa de forma natural, así como cuando se llama al método <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>Animation.finish()</code></a> para que la animación termine inmediatamente.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Nota:</strong> El estado de reproducción <code>\"paused\"</code> reemplaza al estado <code>\"finished\"</code>. Si la animación está pausada y finalizada, el estado<code>\"paused\"</code> será el único reportado. Puedes forzar el estado de la animación a <code>\"finished\"</code> configurando su <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime\" title=\"startTime\"><code>startTime</code></a> a <code>document.timeline.currentTime - (Animation.currentTime * Animation.playbackRate)</code>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> finishHandler <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Animation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onfinish<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nAnimation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onfinish <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> finishHandler<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Una función que debe ser llamada para manejar el evento <code><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/Reference/Events/finish\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">finish</a></code>, o <code>null</code> si no se establece ningún manejador para el evento <code>finish</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>Animation.onfinish</code> es utilizado en varias ocasiones en el juego de Alice in Web Animations API Land <a href=\"https://codepen.io/rachelnabors/pen/PNYGZQ?editors=0010\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Growing/Shrinking Alice Game</a>. Aquí hay una instancia en la que agregamos eventos de puntero a un elemento después de que su animación de opacidad se haya desvanecido:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Agrega una animación a los créditos finales del juego.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> endingUI <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"ending-ui\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> bringUI <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> endingUI<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">animate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>keysFade<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> timingFade<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Pone en Pausa dichos créditos.</span>\nbringUI<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pause</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Esta función elimina los eventos de puntero en los créditos.</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">hide</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>endingUI<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Cuando los créditos se hayan desvanecido,</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// volvemos a agregar los eventos de puntero cuando terminen.</span>\nbringUI<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onfinish</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  endingUI<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>pointerEvents <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'auto'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#dom-animation-onfinish","title":"Web Animations"},{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/web-animations-1/#finish-event","title":"Web Animations"}],"query":"api.Animation.finish_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.Animation.finish_event","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Animations_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web Animations API (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation\"><code>Animation</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>Animation.finish()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxis","id":"sintaxis"},{"text":"Ejemplos","id":"ejemplos"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad con navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_con_navegadores"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"La propiedad onfinish de la interfaz Animation (de la Web Animations API (en-US)) es el manejador de eventos para el evento finish. Este evento se envía cuando la animación termina de reproducirse.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation: finish event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/animation/finish_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/animation/finish_event/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event","title":"Animation.onfinish"}],"pageTitle":"Animation.onfinish - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}